						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab set up in the Hanumān temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>13th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>The record is badly damaged and it seems to register a gift of land and oil to a deity (name lost) by the <hi rend="italic">Seṭṭi, Karaṇas</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Telligas.</hi> All other details are lost. In characters of about the <hi rend="bold">13th Century A.D.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
