<lb n="6" break="no"/>yuṁ jayaśrīyumakku Ida kāyadenda
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḍe kurukṣētragaḷoḷu vāraṇāśiyoḷekkōṭi
<lb n="8"/>kavileyaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kōṭi koṁda <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
